ust here for the chocolate muffins - it's histhird time attending the Summer Gamesafter previously appearing in Tokyo and Rio.)\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999324286927845, \"rank\": 0.0006748878678797168, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"Christiansen\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"the chocolate muffins\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"histhird time\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Gamesafter\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Norwegian swimmer and self-proclaimed \\\"muffin man\\\" seemingly is not the only top athlete obsessed, as a quick scroll will yield countless TikTok videos ofsimilar reviews from fellow Olympiansand their families.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.8235930797592211, \"rank\": 0.21262548001806011, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.862280720129427e-49, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"self-proclaimed \\\"muffin man\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"the only top athlete\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick scroll\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram